
# Intention-Ally: Smart Search & Trend Tracking

## 1. Product Overview
- AI-powered search keyword tracking application
- Automates daily internet searches via Brave Search API
- Collects, summarizes, and visualizes relevant information
- Avoids algorithmic ranking biases

## 2. Core Features
- Daily automated searches (up to 10 keywords)
- Summarized insights and references
- Trend visualization with line charts
- Data privacy focus
- Cost-efficient API usage

## 3. Technical Architecture
### Stack
- Backend: FastAPI (Python)
- Search: Brave Search API
- Database: Supabase
- Frontend: Streamlit UI
- Scheduling: Automated daily cron jobs

### Data Flow
1. User keyword definition
2. Daily automated searches
3. Result processing and storage
4. Trend visualization
5. Automated data cleanup

## 4. Key Components
### Backend (FastAPI)
- Search endpoint integration
- Summary generation
- Trend data processing
- Rate limiting (1 search/day/keyword)

### Frontend (Streamlit)
- Search results dashboard
- Trend visualization
- Data management interface
- Settings configuration

### Data Management
- Efficient storage schema
- Auto-deletion for old records
- Privacy-focused data handling

## 5. Implementation Priorities
- User-friendly interface
- Reliable search automation
- Accurate trend tracking
- Cost optimization
- Data privacy compliance

## 6. Future Enhancements
- Increased keyword limits
